<p>I&#8217;ve picked up something this time which I&#8217;ve always wanted to study properly &#8211; <a href="http://gnus.org/"><em>Gnus</em></a>. The Emacs news and email reader. This is going to be a multipart episode since Gnus is so big. I don&#8217;t know how many exactly but as of now, I&#8217;ve got a 3 part thing planned.</p>

<p>Also, the hiatus was unexpected. Things should be smoother now.</p>

